Chicago Bears Trade Tight End Olsen to Carolina Panthers for Draft Pick

-- B y   R o b   G l o s t e r
-- 
2011-07-29T02:24:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-29/chicago-bears-trade-tight-end-olsen-to-carolina-panthers-for-draft-pick.html
The  Chicago Bears  traded tight end
Greg Olsen to the Carolina Panthers for an undisclosed draft
pick, the Bears said tonight on their website.  Olsen caught 194 passes for 1,981 yards and 20 touchdowns
in four seasons with  Chicago .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rob Gloster at 
 rgloster@bloomberg.net  